name: Tezpunks
description:
Tezpunks

Year AD 7702, a group of deadly punks with superpowers are assigned a mysterious mission.  
Objectives of the mission will be communicated to them from the command center.For now,the only objective communicated to the punks is to time travel to 2021. 

ID #018
Male

Name         : Lomzeth
Strength     : 100/100
Intelligence : 100/100

Lomzeth was a sailor, musician and treasure hunter. Once the sirens lured him with their enchanting music to kill him. Lomzeth responded to the sirens with his music and one of the sirens fell in love with him. Even though Lomzeth jumped into the ocean, sirens instead of killing him, showed him the way to the treasures hidden by them.
